#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an3.52"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.52:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.52:0.2"
msgid "6. Brāhmaṇavagga "
msgstr "6. Brahmins "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.52:0.3"
msgid "52. Dutiyadvebrāhmaṇasutta "
msgstr "52. Two Brahmins (2nd) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli1.156, sc1
msgctxt "an3.52:1.1"
msgid "Atha kho dve brāhmaṇā jiṇṇā vuddhā mahallakā addhagatā vayoanuppattā vīsavassasatikā jātiyā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu. Ekamantaṃ nisinnā kho te brāhmaṇā bhagavantaṃ etadavocuṃ: "
msgstr "Then two old brahmins—elderly and senior, who were advanced in years and had reached the final stage of life, being a hundred and twenty years old—went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, and said to the Buddha: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.52:1.2"
msgid "“mayamassu, bho gotama, brāhmaṇā jiṇṇā vuddhā mahallakā addhagatā vayoanuppattā vīsavassasatikā jātiyā; "
msgstr "“We brahmins, Master Gotama, are old, elderly and senior, we’re advanced in years and have reached the final stage of life; we’re a hundred and twenty years old. "

msgctxt "an3.52:1.3"
msgid "te camhā akatakalyāṇā akatakusalā akatabhīruttāṇā. "
msgstr "And we haven’t done what is good and skillful, nor have we made a shelter from fear. "

msgctxt "an3.52:1.4"
msgid "Ovadatu no bhavaṃ gotamo, anusāsatu no bhavaṃ gotamo yaṃ amhākaṃ assa dīgharattaṃ hitāya sukhāyā”ti. "
msgstr "Advise us, Master Gotama, instruct us! It will be for our lasting welfare and happiness.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an3.52:2.1"
msgid "“Taggha tumhe, brāhmaṇā, jiṇṇā vuddhā mahallakā addhagatā vayoanuppattā vīsavassasatikā jātiyā; "
msgstr "“Indeed, brahmins, you’re old, elderly and senior. "

msgctxt "an3.52:2.2"
msgid "te cattha akatakalyāṇā akatakusalā akatabhīruttāṇā. "
msgstr "And you haven’t done what is good and skillful, nor have you made a shelter from fear. "

msgctxt "an3.52:2.3"
msgid "Āditto kho ayaṃ, brāhmaṇā, loko jarāya byādhinā maraṇena. "
msgstr "This world is burning with old age, sickness, and death. "

msgctxt "an3.52:2.4"
msgid "Evaṃ āditte kho, brāhmaṇā, loke jarāya byādhinā maraṇena, yo idha kāyena saṃyamo vācāya saṃyamo manasā saṃyamo, taṃ tassa petassa tāṇañca leṇañca dīpañca saraṇañca parāyaṇañcāti. "
msgstr "But restraint here by way of body, speech, and mind is the shelter, protection, island, refuge, and haven for the departed. "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an3.52:3.1"
msgid "Ādittasmiṃ agārasmiṃ, "
msgstr "When your house is on fire, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an3.52:3.2"
msgid "yaṃ nīharati bhājanaṃ; "
msgstr "you rescue the pot "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an3.52:3.3"
msgid "Taṃ tassa hoti atthāya, "
msgstr "that’s useful, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an3.52:3.4"
msgid "no ca yaṃ tattha ḍayhati. "
msgstr "not the one that’s burnt. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
#. VAR: Evaṃ āditto kho → evaṃ ādīpito (bj, pts1) | evaṃ ādittake (s1-3, km)
msgctxt "an3.52:4.1"
msgid "Evaṃ āditto kho loko, "
msgstr "And as the world is on fire "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an3.52:4.2"
msgid "jarāya maraṇena ca; "
msgstr "with old age and death, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an3.52:4.3"
msgid "Nīharetheva dānena, "
msgstr "you should rescue by giving, "

#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: sunīhataṃ → sunibbhataṃ (mr)
msgctxt "an3.52:4.4"
msgid "dinnaṃ hoti sunīhataṃ. "
msgstr "for what’s given is rescued. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "an3.52:5.1"
msgid "Yodha kāyena saṃyamo, "
msgstr "The restraint practiced here—"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an3.52:5.2"
msgid "Vācāya uda cetasā; "
msgstr "of body, speech, and mind—"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an3.52:5.3"
msgid "Taṃ tassa petassa sukhāya hoti, "
msgstr "leads the departed to happiness, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an3.52:5.4"
msgid "Yaṃ jīvamāno pakaroti puññan”ti. "
msgstr "as the good deeds done while living.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.52:5.5"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
